                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170115-188-off1027 t18170115-188-crimeloc1030"></join>. On the 30th of December, between five and six o'clock in the evening, I was cleaning my windows, and saw a hand snatch a pair of water-tight shoes from my door; I went out, and the prisoner was secured.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18170115-188-person1357">
                  RICHARD 
                  PORRI
               <interp inst="t18170115-188-person1357" type="surname" value="PORRI"></interp>
