                     <interp inst="t18170115-188-person1357" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I live next door to the prosecutor. On the 30th of December, I was standing at my door, and saw the prisoner before the window; he had nothing in his hand, in a little time I saw him with the shoes; I took him, and he threw them down.</p>
               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>HIGHAM BARNETT. I took the prisoner into custody.</p>
